                <p class="fs-5 mb-4">Privacy Policy For QRCodeScanner.Me!</p>
                <p class="fs-5 mb-4">We prioritize the privacy and security of our users' data above all else. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information when you use our web app and the choices you have associated with that information.</p>
                <h2 class="fw-bolder mb-4 mt-5">Information Collection and Use</h2>
